        "created_at": "2012-02-23T08:36:46.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Well, I have another problem now I cant edit those commands at all. LBA Scene Editor is horribly bugged, for example: I delete an actors life script and paste in a new one that is different, save the changes, check again the script and for some odd reason the original script is STILL there, except garbled up with a few characters from the script I pasted in (which makes the game crash)<br>\nIs there any tool that actually works that lets me edit actor scripts? <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/frowning_face.png?v=12\" title=\":frowning_face:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":frowning_face:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
