      {
        "id": 373020,
        "name": "Jack McKalling",
        "username": "Jack_McKalling",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/jack_mckalling/{size}/624_2.png",
        "created_at": "2012-03-04T22:06:26.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>If you still want to play hard mode in LBA2, you could consider one or more <a href=\"/t/lba-challenge-thread/13829/13\">challenges</a>?</p>\n<p>Its not hard coded features, but if youre truthful to yourself and consistent, these could be alot harder than normal playthrough. Also dont be afraid of using <a href=\"/t/lba1-2-glitchs-bugs/13891/1\">known bugs/glitches</a> <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/stuck_out_tongue.png?v=12\" title=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>Youre not limited to only the proven ones or only the unconfirmed ones, just take any challenge you like, read the description and go ahead. We all (me specifically) would appreciate it if you were able to prove the possibility of one of the red ones, but you dont need to.</p>",
